OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fand overnight will be cloudy with some
OL,7,Fpatchy light rain, this mainly across
OL,8,FArgyll. Some misty low cloud along the
OL,9,Fcoast. Light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FSome drizzly rain across
OL,12,FArgyll in the morning. Otherwise it
OL,13,Fwill be dry with cloud thinning to
OL,14,Fgive some sunshine during the
OL,15,Fafternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
