OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith some sunshine on Thursday
OL,7,Falthough cloudier across Argyll. Dry
OL,8,Fwith plenty of sunshine on Friday.
OL,9,FCloudy start Saturday, brighter later,
OL,10,Fespecially in west. Becoming very warm
OL,11,For hot.
